Regulation (EEC) No 574/72 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in Article 60, paragraphs 5 and 6 shall be deleted;
2. Article 62 shall be replaced by the following:
3. Article 63(2) shall be replaced by the following:
4. in Article 66(1), ‘in Articles 20 and 21’ shall be replaced by ‘in Article 21’;
5. in Article 93(1), ‘22b’ shall be deleted and ‘34a or 34b’ shall be replaced by ‘or 34a’.
